The evidence with the title 'Rate review & the 80/20 rule | healthcare.gov ' says The health care law provides 2 new ways to hold insurance companies accountable and help keep your costs down: rate review and the 80/20 rule.  ... Look up your insurance plan to see its proposed and final rate increase .  ... If you or your employer will get a rebate , your insurance company must notify you by august 1. 
